standard: When you discover a new word, save it in the app, along with its translation
english: When you discover a new word, save it in the app, along with its translation
french: Quand vous tombez sur un nouveau mot d'une langue étrangère, enregistrez-le dans l’application, avec sa traduction

standard: The app will ask you, say, 10 random words each day
english: The app will ask you, say, 10 random words each day
french: Passez ensuite une interro sur vos propres mots

standard: Gardez le rythme d'une interro par jour
english: Keep up the pace of one quiz per day
french: Gardez le rythme d'une interro par jour

standard: As you progress, the words you retain well will be archived
english: As you progress, the words you retain well will be archived
french: Au fur et à mesure des interros, les mots que vous retenez le mieux seront archivés

standard: Those you have difficulties with will be revisited more frequently
english: Those you have difficulties with will be revisited more frequently
french: Les mots difficiles, eux, vous seront demandés plus souvent

standard: And in the end, these words will be in your memory
english: And in the end, these words will be in your memory
french: Et au bout du compte, tous ces mots seront dans votre tête

standard: Do NOT store any sensitive data on this app!
english: Do NOT store any sensitive data on this app!
french: Ne laisser aucune information confidentielle sur cette application !
